Frustrated 52 Wizadress  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uailwyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ailwyn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/9/01 4:02:09 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Won't speak about Golem</span><hr size=1> *sigh* check the walkthrough or the FAQ...Arantir doesn't talk about the golem.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujerrek.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jerrek</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/9/01 5:25:57 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Won't speak about Golem</span><hr size=1> Read his text Ail.. he said he wouldn't talk about the gnome.. not the golem.  (yeh his post title says golem, I'll give you that much)..<br>
<br>
Let's see.. did you un-target Arantir while chatting with him?  Some NPCs won't &quot;hear&quot; you unless you have them targeted.<br>
<br>
Also, I think I recall something about Arantir having a very very low listening range.. you basically have to be standing in his face or sitting on his shoulders before he'll listen to what you have to say to him... assuming you have him targeted. =)<br>
<br>
By now he's de-popped.. so if you already gave him the ring.. you might have to do it again.  Unless you have a buddy wizard that's doing this part.. then tag along with him.. Arantir will hand out multiple gnotes for the gnome. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usarerin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sarerin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/9/01 6:42:25 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Won't speak about Golem</span><hr size=1> Oops i meant the gnome he wouldn't talk to me about not the Golem.  Sorry was typing before morning coffee<br>
